trans-unit.source: Provides run-time access to the routing service to allow dynamic modification of the routing configuration.
trans-unit.target: Gir kjøretid tilgang til tjenesten Ruting å tillate dynamisk endring av ruting konfigurasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Applies a new <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration"></xref> to a running instance of the routing service.
trans-unit.target: Bruker en ny <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration"> </xref> kjører forekomsten av tjenesten som ruting.

trans-unit.source: After calling ApplyConfiguration, the new <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration> only applies to new sessions and messages.
trans-unit.target: Etter å ApplyConfiguration, den nye <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>gjelder bare for nye økter og meldinger.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: > [!WARNING] > Do not modify the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration> object after calling ApplyConfiguration, as <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration> does not provide thread-safe updates or extensions.
trans-unit.target: > [!WARNING] > Ikke endre den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>objekt etter kaller ApplyConfiguration, som <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>leverer ikke sikker oppdateringer eller utvidelser.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: > > If you must perform subsequent updates of the routing configuration, use a new instance of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration> for each update.
trans-unit.target: >> Hvis du må utføre påfølgende oppdateringer av ruting konfigurasjonen, bruker du en ny forekomst av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>for hver oppdatering.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: The routing configuration to be applied.
